# Saleor Configurator — dev/staging ONLY (gitignored via .env*.local)
#
# Copy to .env.configurator.local and paste a staff or broad-permission app token.
# Never commit this file. Never use production admin tokens.
# Never import SALEOR_CONFIGURATOR_TOKEN in Next.js app code.
#
# Generate in Dashboard → Configuration → Staff → [your dev user] → Create token
# or create a dedicated "Configurator Dev" app with required permissions.
#
# SALEOR_CONFIGURATOR_TOKEN=
